{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Fix send button truncated by sidebar viewport (#1617)\n\n* \ud83d\udc1b Fix transparent glass backgrounds across all themes\n\nAll 28 themes used rgba with alpha < 1.0 for glassBackground,\ncausing every glass element (modals, cards, navbar, sidebar) to\nshow content bleeding through. Convert all glassBackground values\nfrom rgba to rgb for fully opaque solid backgrounds.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* \ud83d\udc1b Fix send button truncated by sidebar viewport\n\nAdd flex-shrink-0 to all three send buttons (running, failed, default\nstates) so they don't get squeezed out of the sidebar. Also add\noverflow-hidden to the input wrapper to prevent edge overflow.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
